{"tid":1709274,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大學站及粉嶺與上水路段被擲物   火炭站至大埔站架空電纜受干擾停駛","createTime":"2019-11-12T00:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T01:10:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f49c977b2d7108fc82ebaa3b6fae68f97488e83","tid":1709274,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VZeQDWPaYieRrgY_GNiR.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191112a070425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVZeQDWPaYieRrgY_GNiR.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191112a070425.jpg&h=d4077a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】港鐵表示，東鐵綫大學站附近及介乎粉嶺與上水之間的路段，被人投擲物件，東鐵綫服務受影響。<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺與上水站之間被投擲的物件已清理，至於在大學站附近的仍在處理中。<br />\n<br />\n由於架空電纜運作受干擾，東鐵綫火炭站至大埔站服務，即時暫停。港鐵正安排免費接駁巴士，行走沙田至大埔墟站，請乘客為行程預留充裕乘車時間。<br />\n<br />\n東鐵綫現維持以下服務：<br />\n<br />\n紅磡至火炭站，維持6分鐘一班車<br />\n<br />\n大埔墟至羅湖站，維持15分鐘一班車<br />\n<br />\n大埔墟至落馬洲站，維持15分鐘一班車<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：0703<br />\n<br />\n更新時間：0719"},{"pid":"bed1b167f5112b286bc1c591ff953d32fa8ee945","tid":1709274,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"大學咁多狗都睇唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede1245cc10ede885e65625a2eb0bb668de52440","tid":1709274,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:36:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">架空電纜受干擾 東鐵綫火炭至大埔墟服務即時暫停</span></span></strong><br />\n香港電台-港聞<br />\n香港電台-港聞 <br />\n9.6k 人追蹤<br />\n2019年11月12日 上午7:32<br />\n10 則留言<br />\n港鐵表示，由於架空電纜運作受干擾，東鐵綫火炭至大埔墟服務即時暫停。<br />\n<br />\n在大埔墟站，車上有廣播指大學站發生電力故障。現場所見，列車之後未有開出，乘客離開車廂，秩序大致良好，但未見港鐵職員在場協助。港鐵說，正安排免費接駁巴士，行走沙田至大埔墟站，呼籲乘客預留乘車時間。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵說，目前紅磡至火炭站列車服務維持6分鐘一班，大埔墟至羅湖站維持15分鐘一班車，大埔墟至落馬洲站維持15分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n至於大學站附近及介乎粉嶺與上水之間路段，被人投擲物件，粉嶺與上水之間的物件已清理，但大學站附近的仍在處理中，東鐵綫服務受影響。"},{"pid":"362a07912a11ab51e4a692beca2dc8806b75ae03","tid":1709274,"uid":127791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bed1b167f5112b286bc1c591ff953d32fa8ee945","tid":1709274,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:36:12.000Z","msg":"大學咁多狗都睇唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17035721bdce8b51876f5c7aec27e994bb018c8c","tid":1709274,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:40:07.000Z","msg":"反正今日交通咁順，不如組隊去中環shopping<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1709270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1709270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e90534972840c0d8bf25e15d4008c1cd3b983ecd","tid":1709274,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:40:38.000Z","msg":"跟人民對抗 唔會有好下埸！！"},{"pid":"2d4f99ba5eb9042244619ad4a1835aa5bdb12217","tid":1709274,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"如果用鐵鏈跨過兩條架空電線會唔會short circuit"},{"pid":"5ba0185c20cad926f975ef99b569a3c2f5a3d02d","tid":1709274,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:05:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭幾時忍唔住<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n又出嚟譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8febde783fcafb00d777820c5636dda38166f15","tid":1709274,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"手足搞到人哋返唔到工啦"}]}